---
title: Super Quick Cajun Beef with Mushrooms and Rice
description: Super speedy, this Super Quick Cajun Beef takes only 15 minutes to make. Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix contains ingredients such as chilli powder, ground cumin, oregano and thyme.
